songs.title: Sky High*
songs.lyrics:
Lyrics From Snippet

[Intro]
Your love is sky high, it's so hard to find
Danny, I see you

[Chorus]
Your love is sky high, it's so hard to find
You left me in the blind
Baby girl, your love is sky high, it's so hard to find
You left me in the blind
I don't wanna waste your time
You've been on the blinds, knockin' all these guys
You don't wanna play your mind
